chers from all career stages and disciplinary backgrounds, but especially early-career researchers and students who are struggling with subjectivity, positionality, and the realities of being reflexive.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2023) 0aQualitative research. 0aSocial sciencesxResearch. 0aSociologyxResearch. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertBristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311119663340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781447330882423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781447330882/original  a978-3-11-119663-3  Bristol UP/Policy Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aGBV-deGruyter-alles